22 May 2012Members of the media are hereby advised that the Deputy President's media briefing initially scheduled for Thursday, 24 May 2012 has been postponed.The Deputy President's media briefing which will focus on the Gauteng Freeway Improvement Project, following an update report to Cabinet by the Inter-Ministerial Committee which he chairs will now take place as follows:Members of the media are invited as follows: Date: Thursday, 31 May 2012 Time: 09h00 Venue: Imbizo Media Centre, 120 Plein Street, Cape TownThere will be a video link up to the GCIS Auditorium, 1st Floor, Midtown Building, cnr Sisulu and Madiba Sts, PretoriaRSVP: Proffesor Ndawonde (Pretoria) E-mail: proffesor@gcis.gov.za 0784565738 Sbongile Dalasile (Cape Town) E-mail: sbongile@gcis.gov.za Cell: 0712921006 Enquiries: Jimmy Manyi Cell: 0823793454 Issued by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS)